TTT Enterprise – Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 2025.11.17

1. General Information

TTT Enterprise (“we”, “our”, “the App”) is committed to protecting user privacy.

This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, and protected when using the TTT Enterprise mobile application.

TTT Enterprise is a business productivity application designed to support attendance tracking, work requests, and internal operational workflows for organizations.

2. Information We Collect

We collect only the minimum information required to operate core features.

Account & Usage Information

• User account identifier (such as username or internal ID)
• App usage logs for stability and security
• Device type and operating system version

This information is used solely for system functionality and security.

Location Information (Optional)

If permission is granted, the app may access location data only during specific user actions such as:
• Attendance check-in / check-out
• Work activity confirmation

Important notes:
• Location permission is optional
• Users can deny permission and continue using the app
• The app does not track location in the background
• Location data is not used for advertising or analytics

Request & Attendance Data

• Date and time selections
• Request types (leave, overtime, etc.)
• User-provided notes or attachments

The app does not collect:
• Payment or banking information
• Government-issued identifiers
• Biometric data

3. How We Use Information

Information is used only to:
• Process attendance and work requests
• Support internal business workflows
• Improve system stability and security
• Meet legal or organizational requirements

We do not use data for advertising or resale.

4. Data Sharing

We do not sell or rent user data.

Data may be shared only:
• If required by law
• With trusted infrastructure providers for system operation
• For security or fraud prevention purposes

5. User Rights

Users may:
• Access and review their data
• Request correction of inaccurate information
• Revoke permissions (such as location access)
• Stop using the app at any time

6. Data Security

We apply industry-standard safeguards including:
• Secure data transmission
• Access control and authorization
• Encryption where applicable

7. Policy Updates

This Privacy Policy may be updated as features evolve.
Significant changes will be communicated through official channels.

